{
  "stem": "19055.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 96.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The work in the fields and probably that few months that we spent there-- and we ate relatively well-- help us to survive the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Eventually, we went, went to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was from the end of June or from the beginning of July until late October.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we were working on the fields, somebody whispered to us that there was an assassination against Hitler, which unfortunately failed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We learned that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also learned, I think from the one-armed man, that the Allied landed in Normandy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we learned it later, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when this happened, we were still in, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my memories from this period [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were a mixture of, of relative well-being, being outdoors on the fields and working.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when you know when you work, you know that they're not going to kill you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe we are useful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe they need us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or maybe, maybe it was reassuring to, to have a few people like, like the one-armed Austrian and the mayor with the swastika who was quite decent.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as fall came, the work ended.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gathered us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said goodbye to the farmers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then again, they took us to railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here, we go back to my old friend, the cattle car, the boxcar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, in, in different stations, there more and more people were put in the wagon, so several thousands of people were collected again in a very organized German fashion.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And away we go, several days again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The train was going, as far as I remember, north, day after day, slowing down and going faster.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And again, you have no idea where you're going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It became already colder.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
